For now, the markets are happy there is a deal, says Vivek Sharma, head of international business at Nuvama Asset Services & Nuvama Private. "The politics might be consuming the narrative, but it'll die down. India's been smart to remain ambiguous, remaining aligned with the U.S., without jeopardising its relationship with Russia."

